  <brief_title>Intra Versus Extrahepatic Division of Right Hepatic Vein During Rightsided Hemihepatectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Phase 2 Study of Intra Versus Extrahepatic Division of Right Hepatic Vein During Rightsided Hemihepatectomy</official_title>
